26dfee0daaca7dabf8a624a07de9b0","tid":832193,"uid":180798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"95a614e5ea99fafe41e6d6c8cabe7db3c8adca2f","tid":832193,"uid":13552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"好後悔乜都聽屋企講<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同感 不過唔怪佢地 都係怪自己太無主見 又唔識去選擇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"真 你冇得怪佢地 始終佢地係你屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T05:49:27.000Z","msg":"係㗎<br />\n雖然一方面佢地唔識開解我, 唔會去明我諗乜<br />\n呢個係失望<br />\n但怪自己冇主見, 冇信心企硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好在我最後都「自把自為」得到"},{"pid":"ee11429017104bd79e0e916e50cb2acf473780c5","tid":832193,"uid":103750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:02:46.000Z","msg":"其實真係好矛盾<br />\n我自己想做乜<br />\n同現實比唔比我咁做<br />\n我自己根本唔想讀工程 <br />\n但現實社會自己既興趣科根本屎都冇都食<br />\n而加出到黎做工程都叫做2萬up 養到屋企人<br />\n我認向現實低頭咗<br />\n但我有個frd 好固執一定要讀興趣科 追夢<br />\n讀左20萬degree 仲要借錢<br />\n而加畢左業差唔多一年都未有野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中間日子1星期有一兩日返下part time <br />\n但多蚊日日係屋企問屋企人拎飯錢<br />\n我反而覺得自己好彩冇好似佢咁諗到咁清自己想點<br />\n話唔定當年跟佢咁讀興趣科，我都一樣問緊屋企人拎零用錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff23167327630934b0b88a65a5beef8e464c665","tid":832193,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依家都唔知自己想做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac186a5a9953b5aca312b8b690f2dfce82d9855","tid":832193,"uid":52369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:43:42.000Z","msg":"剩係後悔當初冇讀好書<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e159d4368902675a5a492fac901e60b38b6897cf","tid":832193,"uid":180588,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"細個真係好好讀書 .. 要玩日後大把世界玩....<br />\n我自己都準備出年讀番書...<br />\n因為有學識個世界真係好唔同！"},{"pid":"c7bfbc51b36a0fb38a54e7f9dae0806e3022af06","tid":832193,"uid":92950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85ed503da74e44a8ea8e73e69b25342eb766971f","tid":832193,"uid":180798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b9d69ce80eb19720a5f6ba15fc687f664fd2829","tid":832193,"uid":92950,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"後悔, 但無辦法了<br />\n<br />\n3字頭無希望既過來人上"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:18:58.000Z","msg":"想做邊行，又做緊邊行呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:22:07.000Z","msg":"想做電視電影後期，結果就做左隻ADMIN狗"},{"pid":"ad047740ddcc26c18dd15ea3f31701f7d26a268a","tid":832193,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:48:43.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過如果畀你做咗護士<br />\n你而家都會喺度呻辛苦"}]}